    "Conversations about Education frequently revolved around whether ChatGPT could be used as part of the learning experience and job environment.",
    "For Bard and Search Engines, the discussions centered around how ChatGPT could replace or be integrated as part of search engines.",
    "The results of analyzing the most frequent topics by month indicate that people not only discussed applications of ChatGPT but also talked about ChatGPT-related events.",
    "For instance, in February, Bard and Bing entered the top-5 list for the first time.",
    "This was the month when Google launched its own generative AI named Bard, while Microsoft announced the integration of ChatGPT into its search engine Bing."
